These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, musical, drama
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, folk, pop
1. the fan of folk is the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person watching drama movies is between the fan of pop and the person watching musical movies##2
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Movie-Genre      | musical | drama | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | disco    | pop   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, rugby, baseball
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | drawing    | sudoku        | rock-climbing |
| Sport     | rugby | baseball | swimming         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
3 different games are played: canasta, whist, chess
3 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing canasta is between the owner of the ferret and the person playing chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Game   | whist | canasta     | chess |
| Pet        | ferret  | goldfish | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: papaya, apricot, peach
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goldfish
1. the person eating papaya is the owner of the bird##1
2. the person eating peach is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Food   | apricot  | peach     | papaya |
| Pet           | fish | goldfish | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, reading, sudoku
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, sprite
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | reading | sudoku     | cooking |
| Beverage     | sprite    | almond-milk | milk    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, indian
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, teacher, paramedic
1. the software-developer is between the indian and the dutch##2
2. the dutch is the teacher##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | dutch  | egyptian   | indian        |
| Job         | teacher | software-developer | paramedic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, carrot, pineapple
3 different pets are kept: hamster, goldfish, rabbit
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the owner of the hamster is between the person eating pineapple and the owner of the goldfish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | carrot  | broccoli  | pineapple |
| Pet   | goldfish | hamster | rabbit     |

