.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, western
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, old-henry, bluemaster
1. the person watching satire movies is the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching western movies##2
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | comedy  | satire  |
| Cigar   | aristoff | old-henry | bluemaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
There 3 different types of food: garlic, tomato, corn
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person eating corn and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Food       | corn | garlic | tomato  |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | bus        | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, mirinda
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking fanta is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person drinking iced-tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage         | mirinda | fanta | iced-tea |
| Transport   | quad-bike     | car    | motorbike |

