.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, milk
House: townhouse, art-deco, cape-cod
1. the cape-cod house is between the person drinking fanta and the townhouse house##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | 7up      | milk      |
| House       | art-deco  | cape-cod | townhouse |

