.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, rock, salsa
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, daisy, poppy
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person who growspoppy is between the person who growsiris and the person who growsdaisy##2
3. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | rock   | salsa   |
| Flower         | daisy | poppy | iris |

