.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit, dog
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, gospel, punk
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the dog and the fan of gospel##2
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Pet      | dog | rabbit   | horse |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | disco | gospel   |

 